snippet: Five months after Sarah Palin’s first stint with the channel ended, the former vice-presidential candidate will become a paid contributor.
abstract: Fox News Channel announces that Sarah Palin will return as paid contributor, five months after her initial contract expired; Palin's new contract is expected to be less lucrative than previous one, despite retention of core fan base, due to her declining star power.
lead_paragraph: Five months after Sarah Palin’s first stint with the channel ended, the former vice-presidential candidate will become a paid contributor.

headline.main: Palin Returns to Fox News, After a Brief Split
headline.print_headline: Palin Is Returning to Fox News, Months After They Parted Ways
